latestPosts.caption:
Do not miss the end♥️🥹

The Duden Waterfalls in Antalya, Turkey, are a stunning natural attraction formed by the Düden River from the Taurus Mountains. 

The Upper Düden Waterfall, located northeast of the city, features a cave behind the falls and a peaceful park. 

The Lower Düden Waterfall dramatically drops into the Mediterranean in the Lara district and is best viewed from the sea. Open year-round, these waterfalls are especially beautiful in spring and summer, offering both tranquility and breathtaking coastal views.

#antalya #dudenwaterfalls #turkey #wanderlust #trip2025 #softtransition #transitionreel

This trip reminded me how refreshing it is to step away, breathe in new places, and let nature and city life inspire the soul.✨🫶🏻
